  <brief_title>A Dose Evaluation Study of the Effect of Plug Placement on the Efficacy and Safety of the Latanoprost Punctal Plug Delivery System (L-PPDS) in Subjects With Ocular Hypertension or Open-Angle Glaucoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>PPL GLAU 13: A Randomized Phase 2 Study of the Effect of Plug Placement on Efficacy and Safety of the Latanoprost Punctal Plug Delivery System (L-PPDS) in Subjects With Ocular Hypertension (OH) or Open-Angle Glaucoma (OAG)</official_title>
